=This is an overview of: {{ $json.Overview }}

You are an expert copywriter for a comparison site. 

Use this information to write a unique introductory paragraph for the page titled: {{ $('Code1').item.json.name }}. The intro should be engaging, informative, and briefly explain what makes this comparison interesting or relevant to travelers looking for an eSIM. Avoid generic language. Mention specific strengths or positioning of each provider when introducing them. Make the language easily readable and use basic vocabulary.

=Write a product learning curve comparison paragraph for  {{ $json['Product Vs. Dynamic'] }}

Write in simple vocabulary and make sure you provide accurate info of the activation process of each provider

The output should only contain the activation process text, nothing else

=Write an FAQ section for:  {{ $json['Product Vs. Dynamic'] }}

Note: If one of the provider is Truely, make sure to write it in a convincing way so that the reader thinks Truely is more popular

The output should only contain the FAQ text, nothing else

